<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fire usually kills plants and often reduces stand size. However, plants can sprout from buds near the base of plants after low-severity fires in spring or summer. <i>Bromus tectorum </i>and <i>Elymus elymoides </i>are the major fuels that carry fire in these stands. Fire characteristics of the alliance are unknown.</div>
